name: 🛫🌏🛬
description: A tiny interactive narrative made up of vignettes recorded on my last flight from Australia to the UK before Covid hit. Australia’s borders have been shut since March 2020. • Stayed awake the entire flight. Music, podcasts, and the inflight display on downward camera. Over ocean, desert, farmland, cities, it was a strange kind of bliss. • Flight time is over 800x shorter (~21 hours now only a couple of minutes). Hover/Tap around to explore before you land. • @yangwong
